data.description:
Location is an understatement. This Sagewood Town House has been repainted in multiple areas, touched up prepped for carpet or LVP in the lower level to your liking. Priced to sell AS IS, due to needs carpet in lower level and stairs.  Corner location with easy access to Hwy 82, LR has wood floors, wood tongue & groove finished ceiling, floor to ceiling river-rock stone gas-fireplace, vaulted ceilings, bright kitchen (YOUR new appliances would top it off.)
There is a loft area in the Main Bedroom. Three full bathrooms. Lower walk out level area has laundry room, den area, 3rd bedroom area, mechanical and storage area.  New composite type back step to the fenced yard, yard is surrounded with mature land scape plus 1-car garage with built in shelves. See it today!!
